{"tid":2084893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑有黑暴滲透TVB利用「殺手」劇集等技倆，挑戰國安法。","createTime":"2020-06-29T13:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T13:24:48.000Z","uid":21562,"like":80,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"eaf37121311ea22a459296098a24b1aaf5619169","tid":2084893,"uid":21562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T13:59:53.000Z","msg":"該劇在TVB甫播出第一集，惟內容大多都是高舉風、林、火、山旗幟，黑警消失如風，黑幫犯案如林，殺人如火，罪證如山，同時又有大量暴力殺人場面，明顯鼓吹暴力。不論TVB如何用著名偽人包括黎X祥，陳X演繹殺手等角色，作出非法行為仍能夠逍遙法外，公然挑戰香港司法，有關劇集和對白毫無疑問是指向以暴力手段推翻政權，乘機向香港觀眾宣揚「有不滿，便殺人」的概念。其本質就是「港毒」，與擁護基本法、效忠中國香港特區的原則背道而馳，社會各界須認清問題的嚴重性，不讓「港毒」分子蒙混過關透過劇集騎劫公共平台，宣揚不當政治立場。"},{"pid":"5bc4c1fd79bed79197f99c9279817316a1b20dac","tid":2084893,"uid":21562,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:01:51.000Z","msg":"強烈要求腰斬該政治不正確之劇集！！！！"},{"pid":"df01f20454061e70842640ead747ef7ee0bf03a6","tid":2084893,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025633f26e576674f58f48b2dc098f65d9070680","tid":2084893,"uid":78420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:37:28.000Z","msg":"學條死輔警上崗上綫咁挑骨頭就啱啦！"},{"pid":"51792daeaefdaa021db05e3a68d7048c4e779010","tid":2084893,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"TVB作反<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6766b4816e220d5502a8d2143037b1f3179ed9dd","tid":2084893,"uid":21562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T04:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90856f21d5da618ceca13d9d2ff3087c9d690d06","t